$$
\begin{align*}
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_2 &amp;= \alpha \beta - \alpha \beta = 0, \\
\vec{u}_2^\top \vec{u}_3 &amp;= -\beta \gamma + \beta \gamma = 0, \\
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_3 &amp;= -\alpha \gamma + 2\alpha \gamma - \alpha \gamma = 0.
\end{align*}
$$

取$U = (u_1,u_2,u_3)$, 有

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T M U &amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; 2\alpha &amp; \alpha \\
\beta &amp; 0 &amp; -\beta \\
-\gamma &amp; \gamma &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
2m &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 2m &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2m
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \beta &amp; -\gamma \\
2\alpha &amp; 0 &amp; \gamma \\
\alpha &amp; -\beta &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
12m \alpha^2 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 4m \beta^2 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 6m \gamma^2
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= I
\end{align*}
$$

需要取

$$\alpha = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt {3m} }},\beta = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }},\gamma = \pm \frac{1}{{\sqrt {6m} }}$$

另一方面

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T K U &amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; 2\alpha &amp; \alpha \\
\beta &amp; 0 &amp; -\beta \\
-\gamma &amp; \gamma &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
3k &amp; -k &amp; 0 \\
-k &amp; 2k &amp; -k \\
0 &amp; -k &amp; 3k
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha &amp; \beta &amp; -\gamma \\
2\alpha &amp; 0 &amp; \gamma \\
\alpha &amp; -\beta &amp; -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
6\alpha^2 k &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 6\beta^2 k &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 12\gamma^2 k
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{k}{2m} &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \frac{3k}{2m} &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{2k}{m}
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= \Lambda
\end{align*}
$$

此时有

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_1 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{3m}} \\ \frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_2 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \\ 0 \\ -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} \end{pmatrix} \\
\vec{u}_3 &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\ \frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\ -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \end{pmatrix}
\end{cases}
$$"><p>逐一验证</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="29.255ex" height="9.063ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 \begin{align*}
\begin{bmatrix}
2m &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 2m &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2m
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}+ 
\begin{bmatrix}
3k &amp; -k &amp; 0 \\
-k &amp; 2k &amp; -k \\
0 &amp; -k &amp; 3k
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{bmatrix} = 
\begin{bmatrix}
2F_1(t) - F_2(t) \\
F_2(t) - F_3(t) \\
F_3(t) - 2F_4(t)
\end{bmatrix} =
\begin{bmatrix}
2F_1(t) \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

进行合同变换

$$
{U^T}MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + {U^T}KU\vec \eta = {U^T}\vec F
$$

因此

$$
I \ddot{\vec{\eta}} + \Lambda \eta = U^T F = \begin{pmatrix}
\frac{F_1(t)}{\sqrt{3m}} \\
\frac{F_1(t)}{\sqrt{m}} \\
-\frac{2 F_1(t)}{\sqrt{6m}}
\end{pmatrix}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{cases}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \frac{k}{2m} \eta_1 &amp;= \frac{F_0}{\sqrt{3m}} \cos 0.7t, \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \frac{3k}{2m} \eta_2 &amp;= \frac{F_0}{\sqrt{m}} \cos 0.7t, \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \frac{2k}{m} \eta_3 &amp;= -\frac{2F_0}{\sqrt{6m}} \cos 0.7t.
\end{cases}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &amp;= \frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{3} k - 0.98\sqrt{3} m} \cos 0.7t, \\
\eta_2 &amp;= \frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{3k - 0.98m} \cos 0.7t, \\
\eta_3 &amp;= \frac{\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{6} k - 0.245\sqrt{6} m} \cos 0.7t.
\end{cases}
$$

代回

$$
\begin{align*}
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} &amp;=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3m}} &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{3}k - 0.98\sqrt{3}m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{6}k - 0.245\sqrt{6}m}\cos(0.7t)
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp; =
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) + \frac{2F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{2F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) + \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{2F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t)
\end{pmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

替换频率为1.4 rad/s

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} =
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3m}} &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{3}k - 3.92\sqrt{3}m}\cos(1.4t) \\
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{3k - 3.92m}\cos(1.4t) \\
\frac{\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{6}k - 0.98\sqrt{6}m}\cos(1.4t)

\begin{pmatrix}
2m &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 2m &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2m
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{pmatrix}+
\begin{pmatrix}
3k &amp; -k &amp; 0 \\
-k &amp; 2k &amp; -k \\
0 &amp; -k &amp; 3k
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix}=
\begin{pmatrix}
2F_1(t) - F_2(t) \\
F_2(t) - F_3(t) \\
F_3(t) - 2F_4(t)
\end{pmatrix}=
\begin{pmatrix}
2F_1(t) - F_2(t) \\
F_2(t) - F_1(t) \\
F_1(t)
\end{pmatrix}
$$

进行合同变换

$$
{U^T}MU\ddot {\vec \eta} + {U^T}KU\vec \eta = {U^T}\vec F
$$

因此

$$
I\ddot{\vec{\eta}} + \Lambda \vec{\eta} = U^T \vec{F} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{F_1(t)}{2\sqrt{3m}} + \frac{F_2(t)}{2\sqrt{3m}} \\
\frac{F_1(t)}{2\sqrt{m}} - \frac{F_2(t)}{2\sqrt{m}} \\
-\frac{4F_1(t)}{\sqrt{6m}} + \frac{2F_2(t)}{\sqrt{6m}}
\end{pmatrix}
$$

可得

$$
\begin{cases}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \frac{k}{2m}\eta_1 &amp;= \frac{0.12F_0}{\sqrt{3m}}\left[ r(t) - r(t - 10) \right] \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \frac{3k}{2m}\eta_2 &amp;= -\frac{0.02F_0}{\sqrt{m}}\left[ r(t) - r(t - 10) \right] \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \frac{2k}{m}\eta_3 &amp;= -\frac{0.12F_0}{\sqrt{6m}}\left[ r(t) - r(t - 10) \right]
\end{cases}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 &amp;= \frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{3} k - 0.98\sqrt{3} m} \cos 0.7t, \\
\eta_2 &amp;= \frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{3k - 0.98m} \cos 0.7t, \\
\eta_3 &amp;= \frac{\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{6} k - 0.245\sqrt{6} m} \cos 0.7t.
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
\begin{pmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{pmatrix} &amp;=
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; \frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3m}} &amp; 0 &amp; \frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}} \\
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{3m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{2\sqrt{m}} &amp; -\frac{1}{\sqrt{6m}}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{3}k - 0.98\sqrt{3}m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{2\sqrt{m} F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{\sqrt{m} F_0}{\sqrt{6}k - 0.245\sqrt{6}m}\cos(0.7t)
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp; =
\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) + \frac{2F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{2F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) + \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t) \\
\frac{F_0}{3k - 2.94m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{2F_0}{3k - 0.98m}\cos(0.7t) - \frac{F_0}{6k - 1.47m}\cos(0.7t)
\end{pmatrix}
\end{align*}
$$

\frac{F_0}{10}
\end{bmatrix}
\left[ r(t) - r(t - 10) \right]
\end{equation}
$$

令$y(t) = U\eta (t) = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{u_r}{\eta _r}(t)} = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{\eta _r}(t){u_r}}$

有

$${U^T}MU\ddot \eta {\rm{ + }}{U^T}KU\eta = {U^T}Q$$

激励为

$$
\begin{equation}
Q = \frac{F_0}{10m}[r(t) - r(t - 10)]
\begin{bmatrix}
-0.4 \\
0.4 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
= \frac{F_0}{10m}
\begin{bmatrix}
-0.4 \\
0.4 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
r(t) - \frac{F_0}{10m}
\begin{bmatrix}
-0.4 \\
0.4 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
r(t - 10)
\end{equation}
$$

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n u_r \eta_r(t) \\

\end{bmatrix}

&amp;= \frac{F_0}{10m} \left( \frac{1}{6} \frac{1}{0.5}
\begin{bmatrix}

\end{bmatrix}

&amp;= \frac{F_0}{10m} \left( \frac{1.4}{3}
\begin{bmatrix}

1
\end{bmatrix} + \frac{-1.4}{3}
\begin{bmatrix}

\end{bmatrix} + \frac{0.2}{6}

&amp;\approx \frac{F_0}{10m}
\begin{bmatrix}

\end{bmatrix}
\left( \left( t - \frac{\sin \omega_r t}{\omega_r} \right) \mu(t) - \left( t - 10 - \frac{\sin \omega_r (t - 10)}{\omega_r} \right) \mu(t - 10) \right)
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix} + 0.1
\begin{bmatrix}
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 0 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -1 \\
0 &amp; -1 &amp; 2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{y}_1 \\
\dot{y}_2 \\
\dot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix} + \frac{k}{m}
\begin{bmatrix}
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 0 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -1 \\
0 &amp; -1 &amp; 2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{bmatrix} =
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation}
$$

令

$$
y(t) = U\eta (t) = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{u_r}{\eta _r}(t)} = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{\eta _r}(t){u_r}} 
$$

$$\eta (t) = {U^{ - 1}}y(t) = {U^T}My(t)$$

则有

$${U^T}MU\ddot \eta {\rm{ + }}{U^T}CU + {U^T}KU\eta = 0$$

$${\ddot \eta _r}{\rm{ + 0}}{\rm{.1}}\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k}{\dot \eta _r} + \omega _r^2{\eta _r} = 0$$

其中

$${\omega _1} \approx 0.77\sqrt {\frac{k}{m}} ,{\omega _2} \approx 1.41\sqrt {\frac{k}{m}} ,{\omega _3} \approx 1.85\sqrt {\frac{k}{m}} ,{u_1} = \frac{1}{2}{[1,\sqrt 2 ,1]^T},{u_2} = \frac{{\sqrt 2 }}{2}{[1,0, - 1]^T},{u_3} = \frac{1}{2}{[1, - \sqrt 2 ,1]^T}$$

$${\xi _r} = \frac{{{c_r}}}{{2{m_r}{\omega _r}}} = \frac{1}{{2{\omega _r}}}0.1\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k} = \frac{{m{\omega _r}}}{{20k}}$$

$${\omega _{rd}} = \sqrt {1 - \xi _r^2} {\omega _r}$$

初始条件为

$$\eta (0) = {U^T}My(0),\dot \eta (0) = {U^T}M\dot y(0)$$

假设为欠阻尼, 则响应为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n \eta_r(t) u_r \\
&amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n e^{-\xi \omega_r t} \left( u_r^\top M y(0) \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{u_r^\top M \dot{y}(0) + \xi_r \omega_r u_r^\top M y(0)}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) u_r \\
&amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n e^{-\xi \omega_r t} \left( u_r^\top M y(0) \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) + u_r^\top M \dot{y}(0) \frac{1}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) u_r
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}
$$

\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n e^{-\xi \omega_r t} \left( u_r^\top M y(0) \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) + u_r^\top M \dot{y}(0) \frac{1}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) u_r \\
&amp;= \frac{e^{-\xi_1 \omega_1 t}}{4} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\left( \cos \omega_{1d} t + \frac{\xi_1 \omega_1}{\omega_{1d}} \sin \omega_{1d} t \right)
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;\quad + \frac{e^{-\xi_2 \omega_2 t}}{2} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\left( \cos \omega_{2d} t + \frac{\xi_2 \omega_2}{\omega_{2d}} \sin \omega_{2d} t \right)
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;\quad + \frac{e^{-\xi_3 \omega_3 t}}{4} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\left( \cos \omega_{3d} t + \frac{\xi_3 \omega_3}{\omega_{3d}} \sin \omega_{3d} t \right)
\begin{bmatrix}

-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;= \frac{\sqrt{2}}{4} e^{-\xi_1 \omega_1 t} \left( \cos \omega_{1d} t + \frac{\xi_1 \omega_1}{\omega_{1d}} \sin \omega_{1d} t \right)
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{4} e^{-\xi_3 \omega_3 t} \left( \cos \omega_{3d} t + \frac{\xi_3 \omega_3}{\omega_{3d}} \sin \omega_{3d} t \right)
\begin{bmatrix}

-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}

初始条件: $y(0) = 0,\dot y(0) = {[0,0,1]^T}$

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n e^{-\xi \omega_r t} \left( u_r^\top M y(0) \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) + u_r^\top M \dot{y}(0) \frac{1}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) u_r \\
&amp;= \frac{e^{-\xi_1 \omega_1 t}}{4} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{\omega_{1d}} \sin \omega_{1d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;\quad + \frac{e^{-\xi_2 \omega_2 t}}{2} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{\omega_{2d}} \sin \omega_{2d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;\quad + \frac{e^{-\xi_3 \omega_3 t}}{4} \left(
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{\omega_{3d}} \sin \omega_{3d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{4\omega_{1d}} e^{-\xi_1 \omega_1 t} \sin \omega_{1d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
-\frac{1}{2\omega_{2d}} e^{-\xi_2 \omega_2 t} \sin \omega_{2d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix} \\
&amp;\quad - \frac{1}{4\omega_{3d}} e^{-\xi_3 \omega_3 t} \sin \omega_{3d} t
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}
$$

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+0.1
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{3}{2} &amp; -\frac{1}{2} &amp; 0 \\
-\frac{1}{2} &amp; 1 &amp; -\frac{1}{2} \\
0 &amp; -\frac{1}{2} &amp; \frac{3}{2}
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{y}_1 \\
\dot{y}_2 \\
\dot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+\frac{k}{m}
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{3}{2} &amp; -\frac{1}{2} &amp; 0 \\
-\frac{1}{2} &amp; 1 &amp; -\frac{1}{2} \\
0 &amp; -\frac{1}{2} &amp; \frac{3}{2}
\end{bmatrix}= 
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{F_0}{m} \cos 0.7t \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation}
$$

令

$$y(t) = U\eta (t) = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{u_r}{\eta _r}(t)} = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{\eta _r}(t){u_r}}$$

则有

$${U^T}MU\ddot \eta {\rm{ + }}{U^T}CU\dot \eta + {U^T}KU\eta = {U^T}Q$$

所以有

$${\ddot \eta _r}{\rm{ + 0}}{\rm{.1}}\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k}{\dot \eta _r}{\rm{ + }}\omega _r^2{\eta _r} = u_r^TF\cos \omega t$$

其中

$${\xi _r} = \frac{{{c_r}}}{{2{m_r}{\omega _r}}} = \frac{1}{{2{\omega _r}}}0.1\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k} = \frac{{m{\omega _r}}}{{20k}}$$

解为

$$
\begin{align}
{\eta _r}(t) &amp;= \frac{{u_r^TF}}{{\omega _r^2\sqrt {{{\left( {1 - \mathop \lambda \nolimits_r^2 } \right)}^2} + {{\left( {2{\lambda _r}{\xi _r}} \right)}^2}} }}\cos \left( {\omega t - {\varphi _r}} \right)\\
{\varphi _r} &amp;= \arctan \left( {\frac{{2{\lambda _r}{\xi _r}}}{{1 - \mathop \lambda \nolimits_r^2 }}} \right)
\end{align}
$$

所以稳态响应为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n u_r \eta_r(t) = \sum_{r = 1}^n \frac{u_r}{\omega_r^2 \sqrt{\left(1 - \lambda_r^2\right)^2 + \left(2 \lambda_r \xi_r\right)^2}} u_r^\top 
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{F}{m} \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \\
&amp;= \frac{F}{m}\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \left(
\frac{\frac{1}{6}\begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{0.5\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{0.5}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 0.5 \cdot \frac{0.71}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. + \frac{\frac{1}{2}\begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; 0 &amp; -1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{1.5\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{1.5}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 1.5 \cdot \frac{1.22}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; 0 &amp; -1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. + \frac{\frac{1}{3}\begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{2\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{2}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 2 \cdot \frac{1.41}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right) \\
&amp;= \frac{F}{m}\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \left( 8.21 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 1 \end{bmatrix} + 0.48 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ -1 \end{bmatrix} + 0.21 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ -1 \\ 1 \end{bmatrix} \right) \\
&amp;= \begin{bmatrix} 8.90 \\ 16.21 \\ 7.94 \end{bmatrix} \frac{F}{m} \cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \\
\varphi_r &amp;= \arctan \left(\frac{2\omega_r^2 \frac{m \omega_r}{20k}}{1 - \lambda_r^2}\right) = \arctan \left(\frac{m \omega_r^3}{10k \left(1 - \lambda_r^2\right)}\right)
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}
$$

$$g(t) = \frac{1}{k}\left( {1 - {e^{ - \xi {\omega _n}t}}\left( {\cos {\omega _d}t + \frac{{\xi {\omega _n}}}{{{\omega _d}}}\sin {\omega _d}t} \right)} \right)$$

系统方程为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+0.1
\begin{bmatrix}
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 0 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -1 \\
0 &amp; -1 &amp; 2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{y}_1 \\
\dot{y}_2 \\
\dot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+\frac{k}{m}
\begin{bmatrix}
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 0 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -1 \\
0 &amp; -1 &amp; 2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y_1 \\
y_2 \\
y_3
\end{bmatrix}= 
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{F_0}{m} \left[ \mu(t) - \mu(t - 5) \right]
\end{equation}
$$

令

$$y(t) = U\eta (t) = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{u_r}{\eta _r}(t)} = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{\eta _r}(t){u_r}}$$

则有

$${U^T}MU\ddot \eta {\rm{ + }}{U^T}CU\dot \eta + {U^T}KU\eta = {U^T}Q$$

所以

$${\ddot \eta _r}{\rm{ + 0}}{\rm{.1}}\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k}{\dot \eta _r}{\rm{ + }}\omega _r^2{\eta _r} = u_r^TF\cos \omega t$$

其中

$${\xi _r} = \frac{{{c_r}}}{{2{m_r}{\omega _r}}} = \frac{1}{{2{\omega _r}}}0.1\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k} = \frac{{m{\omega _r}}}{{20k}}$$

$${\omega _{rd}} = \sqrt {1 - \xi _r^2} {\omega _r}$$

因此

$${\ddot \eta _r}{\rm{ + 0}}{\rm{.1}}\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k}{\dot \eta _r}{\rm{ + }}\omega _r^2{\eta _r} = u_r^TQ$$

解为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &amp;= \sum_{r = 1}^n u_r \eta_r(t) = \sum_{r = 1}^n u_r \frac{F_0}{m} u_r^\top 
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{\omega_r^2} \left( \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r t} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) \right) \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. - \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r (t - 5)} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} (t - 5) + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} (t - 5) \right) \right) \right) \\
&amp;= \frac{F_0}{m} \left( \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r t} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) \right) \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. - \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r (t - 5)} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} (t - 5) + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} (t - 5) \right) \right) \right) \\
&amp;\quad \cdot \left( \frac{1}{4} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; \sqrt{2} &amp; 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{2 - \sqrt{2}} + \frac{1}{2} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; 0 &amp; -1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{2} \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. + \frac{1}{4} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; -\sqrt{2} &amp; 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\frac{1}{2 + \sqrt{2}} \right) \\
&amp;= \frac{F_0}{m} \left( \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r t} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} t + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} t \right) \right) \right. \\
&amp;\quad \left. - \left( 1 - e^{-\xi_r \omega_r (t - 5)} \left( \cos \omega_{rd} (t - 5) + \frac{\xi_r \omega_r}{\omega_{rd}} \sin \omega_{rd} (t - 5) \right) \right) \right) \\
&amp;\quad \cdot \left( \frac{\sqrt{2}}{8} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
-\frac{1}{4} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
0 \\
-1
\end{bmatrix}
-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{8} 
\begin{bmatrix}
1 \\
-\sqrt{2} \\
1
\end{bmatrix}
\right) \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{4} 
\begin{bmatrix}
-1 \\
2 \\
1

div.data-content:
逐一验证

$$
\begin{align*}
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_2 &= \alpha \beta - \alpha \beta = 0, \\
\vec{u}_2^\top \vec{u}_3 &= -\beta \gamma + \beta \gamma = 0, \\
\vec{u}_1^\top \vec{u}_3 &= -\alpha \gamma + 2\alpha \gamma - \alpha \gamma = 0.
\end{align*}
$$

取$U = (u_1,u_2,u_3)$, 有

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T M U &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & 2\alpha & \alpha \\
\beta & 0 & -\beta \\
-\gamma & \gamma & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
2m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 2m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 2m
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & \beta & -\gamma \\
2\alpha & 0 & \gamma \\
\alpha & -\beta & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
12m \alpha^2 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 4m \beta^2 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 6m \gamma^2
\end{pmatrix} \\
&= I
\end{align*}
$$

需要取

$$\alpha = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt {3m} }},\beta = \pm \frac{1}{{2\sqrt m }},\gamma = \pm \frac{1}{{\sqrt {6m} }}$$

另一方面

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T K U &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\alpha & 2\alpha & \alpha \\
\beta & 0 & -\beta \\
-\gamma & \gamma & -\gamma
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
3k & -k & 0 \\
-k & 2k & -k \\

系统方程为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{bmatrix}
1 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 1 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 1
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y}_1 \\
\ddot{y}_2 \\
\ddot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+0.1
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{3}{2} & -\frac{1}{2} & 0 \\
-\frac{1}{2} & 1 & -\frac{1}{2} \\
0 & -\frac{1}{2} & \frac{3}{2}
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{y}_1 \\
\dot{y}_2 \\
\dot{y}_3
\end{bmatrix}
+\frac{k}{m}
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{3}{2} & -\frac{1}{2} & 0 \\
-\frac{1}{2} & 1 & -\frac{1}{2} \\
0 & -\frac{1}{2} & \frac{3}{2}
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{F_0}{m} \cos 0.7t \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation}
$$

令

$$y(t) = U\eta (t) = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{u_r}{\eta _r}(t)} = \sum\limits_{r = 1}^n {{\eta _r}(t){u_r}}$$

则有

$${U^T}MU\ddot \eta {\rm{ + }}{U^T}CU\dot \eta + {U^T}KU\eta = {U^T}Q$$

所以有

$${\ddot \eta _r}{\rm{ + 0}}{\rm{.1}}\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k}{\dot \eta _r}{\rm{ + }}\omega _r^2{\eta _r} = u_r^TF\cos \omega t$$

其中

$${\xi _r} = \frac{{{c_r}}}{{2{m_r}{\omega _r}}} = \frac{1}{{2{\omega _r}}}0.1\frac{{m\omega _r^2}}{k} = \frac{{m{\omega _r}}}{{20k}}$$

解为

$$
\begin{align}
{\eta _r}(t) &= \frac{{u_r^TF}}{{\omega _r^2\sqrt {{{\left( {1 - \mathop \lambda \nolimits_r^2 } \right)}^2} + {{\left( {2{\lambda _r}{\xi _r}} \right)}^2}} }}\cos \left( {\omega t - {\varphi _r}} \right)\\
{\varphi _r} &= \arctan \left( {\frac{{2{\lambda _r}{\xi _r}}}{{1 - \mathop \lambda \nolimits_r^2 }}} \right)
\end{align}
$$

所以稳态响应为

$$
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}
y(t) &= \sum_{r = 1}^n u_r \eta_r(t) = \sum_{r = 1}^n \frac{u_r}{\omega_r^2 \sqrt{\left(1 - \lambda_r^2\right)^2 + \left(2 \lambda_r \xi_r\right)^2}} u_r^\top
\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{F}{m} \\
0 \\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \\
&= \frac{F}{m}\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \left(
\frac{\frac{1}{6}\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{0.5\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{0.5}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 0.5 \cdot \frac{0.71}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & 1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right. \\
&\quad \left. + \frac{\frac{1}{2}\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{1.5\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{1.5}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 1.5 \cdot \frac{1.22}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right. \\
&\quad \left. + \frac{\frac{1}{3}\begin{bmatrix} 1 & -1 & 1 \end{bmatrix}^\top}{2\sqrt{\left(1 - \frac{0.7^2}{2}\right)^2 + \left(2 \cdot 2 \cdot \frac{1.41}{20}\right)^2}} \begin{bmatrix} 1 & -1 & 1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 0 \end{bmatrix} \right) \\
&= \frac{F}{m}\cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \left( 8.21 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 1 \end{bmatrix} + 0.48 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ -1 \end{bmatrix} + 0.21 \begin{bmatrix} 1 \\ -1 \\ 1 \end{bmatrix} \right) \\
&= \begin{bmatrix} 8.90 \\ 16.21 \\ 7.94 \end{bmatrix} \frac{F}{m} \cos \left(0.7t - \varphi_r\right) \\
\varphi_r &= \arctan \left(\frac{2\omega_r^2 \frac{m \omega_r}{20k}}{1 - \lambda_r^2}\right) = \arctan \left(\frac{m \omega_r^3}{10k \left(1 - \lambda_r^2\right)}\right)
\end{aligned}
\end{equation}
$$
